baseline.value: Ayedas - 97% Uludag - 95% Meram - 76% Gediz - 94% Toroslar - 88% Menderes - 94% Osmangazi - 91% Akdeniz - 92%

target.value: Ayedas - 99% Uludag - 98% Meram - 81% Gediz - 97% Toroslar - 92% Menderes - 97% Osmangazi - 94%, Akdeniz - 95%

actual.value: Ayedas – 103.85%, Uludag - 97%, Meram - 93%, Gediz – 98.37%, Toroslar – 99.7%, Menderes - 98.5%, Osmangazi - 96%, Akdeniz – 95.97%

comment.narrative: Menderes was dropped from the list of sub-projects on account of its transfer to the private investor.
